(21, 1, '2010-09-27 01:30:33', '2010-09-27 01:30:33', 'Dermatology involves cutaneous surgery. We employ plastic surgical techniques to ensure the optimum scar appearance.  A small number of our surgical services are list below please call us at (253) 572-2842 with questions or to make an apointment.\r\n\r\n<strong>Mole Removal</strong> - We use dermoscopy, a new non-invasive handheld microscope to view moles, and more accurately identify cancerous lesions prior to removal.\r\n\r\n<strong>Skin Cancer Surgery</strong>\r\n\r\n<strong>Skin Flaps and Grafts</strong>\r\n\r\n<strong>Scar Repair</strong>\r\n\r\n<strong>Keloid Treatments - </strong>Often a combination of steroid injection, surgical removal, and the latest evidence based topical therapies to prevent recurrence.', 'Surgical', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'surgical', '', '', '2011-09-17 18:40:54', '2011-09-17 18:40:54', '', 17, 'http://www.pacedermatology.com', 0, 'page', '', 0),
