(209, 1, '2012-02-26 23:46:17', '2012-02-26 23:46:17', 'We are in the B building (the building closest to the ER) on the Allenmore campus in Suite 3003 just before you go across the bridge to the hospital.\n\n[map width="480" height="320" zoom="14" type="ROADMAP"]\n[marker address="1901 South Union Avenue, Tacoma, WA 98405"]Pace Dermatology<br />1901 South Union Avenue, Tacoma, WA 98405[/marker]\n[/map]\n\nFrom I-5 North or South</strong>\nTake the exit for highway 16 then take the Union Ave. exit and make a right onto Union. Go several blocks until you pass the hospital complex on the right, then turn right on 19th Street. Turn into the Allenmore complex off 19th and park close to the biggest building with the yellow tinted windows, this is the Allenmore B Building. We are on the third floor in suite 3003.\n<strong>\nFrom the west on Highway 16</strong>\nTake the Union Ave. exit and make a left onto Union. Go several blocks until you pass the hospital complex on the right, then turn right on 19th Street. Turn into the Allenmore complex off 19th and park close to the biggest building with the yellow tinted windows, this is the Allenmore B Building. We are on the third floor in suite 3003.\n\n<a href="http://www.pacedermatology.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/03/Allenmore-Building-B.jpg"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-373" title="Allenmore Building B" src="http://www.pacedermatology.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/03/Allenmore-Building-B.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="162" /></a>\n<strong>', 'Map and Directions', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '33-autosave', '', '', '2012-02-26 23:46:17', '2012-02-26 23:46:17', '', 33, 'http://www.pacedermatology.com/33-autosave', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
