(240, 1, '2010-10-18 02:51:34', '2010-10-18 02:51:34', 'All of these photos represent a condition or descriptive term in dermatology.  I have been collecting these photos when something catches my intention.  I started in 2005 when I first had the idea and have collected quite a few images since then.  Photography and dermatology go hand in hand.  It is a very visual field of medicine and lends itself well to the photographer inside us.  I hope these images provide you insight in to the many and varied dermatologic disease processes.  The “acne” photo (a geyser in Yellowstone) is one of my favorites.  Click on the photos at the top to open a slideshow with descriptions.  Some of these photos and others will be decorating the office as well.', '', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', '240', '', '', '2013-01-16 11:31:12', '2013-01-16 18:31:12', '', 0, 'http://www.pacedermatology.com/?p=240', 18, 'nav_menu_item', '', 0),
