(355, 1, '2010-12-31 22:05:50', '2010-12-31 22:05:50', 'Indoor tanning is one of the worst things you can do to your skin.  It dramatically increases your risk of skin cancer.  The beds themselves emit a broad spectrum of UV rays.  There are no standardized safety precautions in the industry.  And recently, there has been a tax levied on their use.  So please avoid skin cancer and premature photo aging by not using tanning beds.', 'Indoor Tanning Harms Your Skin', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'indoor-tanning-harms-your-skin', '', '', '2010-12-31 22:05:50', '2010-12-31 22:05:50', '', 0, 'http://www.pacedermatology.com/?p=355', 0, 'post', '', 0),
