(390, 1, '2010-10-21 12:11:41', '2010-10-21 12:11:41', 'All of these photos represent a condition or descriptive term in dermatology.  I have been collecting these photos when something catches my intention.  I started in 2005 when I first had the idea and have collected quite a few images since then.  Photography and dermatology go hand in hand.  It is a very visual field of medicine and lends itself well to the photographer inside us.  I hope these images provide you insight in to the many and varied dermatologic disease processes.  The "acne" photo (a geyser in Yellowstone) is one of my favorites.  Click on the photos at the top to open a slideshow with descriptions.  Some of these photos and others will be decorating the office as well.\r\n[nggallery id=1]', 'Art', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '184-revision-30', '', '', '2010-10-21 12:11:41', '2010-10-21 12:11:41', '', 184, 'http://www.pacedermatology.com/184-revision-30', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(393, 1, '2010-10-11 03:51:35', '2010-10-11 03:51:35', 'Dr. Pace began the practice and plans to open July of 2011.  He  graduated from Steilacoom high school and went Occidental College in Los  Angeles, California, then went medical school at Loyola University  Chicago, Stritch School of Medicine.  After medical school he completed  his internship at MacNeal Hospital in Berwyn, Illinois prior to  beginning his dermatology residency.  Dr. Pace returned to Loyola for  his dermatology residency in Chicago, Illinois.  Now he has returned to  practice dermatology and serve the community that he grew up in.\r\n\r\nOn a more personal note, Dr. Pace enjoys spending time with his wife and two girls.', 'The Doctor', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '26-revision-7', '', '', '2010-10-11 03:51:35', '2010-10-11 03:51:35', '', 26, 'http://www.pacedermatology.com/26-revision-7', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(394, 1, '2011-04-05 12:50:06', '2011-04-05 12:50:06', '[caption id="attachment_391" align="alignnone" width="200" caption="Aaron K. Pace, M.D."]<a href="http://www.pacedermatology.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/04/Aaron-Headshot.jpg"><img class="size-thumbnail wp-image-391" title="Dr. Pace" src="http://www.pacedermatology.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/04/Aaron-Headshot-200x168.jpg" alt="" width="200" height="168" /></a>[/caption]\r\n\r\nDr. Pace began the practice and plans to open July of 2011.  He  graduated from Steilacoom high school and went Occidental College in Los  Angeles, California, then went medical school at Loyola University  Chicago, Stritch School of Medicine.  After medical school he completed  his internship at MacNeal Hospital in Berwyn, Illinois prior to  beginning his dermatology residency.  Dr. Pace returned to Loyola for  his dermatology residency in Chicago, Illinois.  Now he has returned to  practice dermatology and serve the community that he grew up in.\r\n\r\nOn a more personal note, Dr. Pace enjoys spending time with his wife and two girls.', 'The Doctor', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '26-revision-8', '', '', '2011-04-05 12:50:06', '2011-04-05 12:50:06', '', 26, 'http://www.pacedermatology.com/26-revision-8', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
