(412, 1, '2011-04-05 12:51:05', '2011-04-05 12:51:05', '[caption id="attachment_391" align="alignnone" width="200" caption="Aaron K. Pace, M.D."]<a href="http://www.pacedermatology.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/04/Aaron-Headshot.jpg"><img class="size-thumbnail wp-image-391" title="Dr. Pace" src="http://www.pacedermatology.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/04/Aaron-Headshot-200x168.jpg" alt="" width="200" height="168" /></a>[/caption]\r\n\r\nDr. Pace began the practice and plans to open July of 2011.  He  graduated from Steilacoom high school and went Occidental College in Los  Angeles, California, then went medical school at Loyola University  Chicago, Stritch School of Medicine.  After medical school he completed  his internship at MacNeal Hospital in Berwyn, Illinois prior to  beginning his dermatology residency.  Dr. Pace returned to Loyola for  his dermatology residency in Chicago, Illinois.  Now he has returned to  practice dermatology and serve the community that he grew up in.\r\n\r\nOn a more personal note, Dr. Pace enjoys spending time with his wife, two daughters, and their dogs.', 'The Doctor', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '26-revision-9', '', '', '2011-04-05 12:51:05', '2011-04-05 12:51:05', '', 26, 'http://www.pacedermatology.com/26-revision-9', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
