(436, 1, '2013-01-01 22:04:26', '2013-01-02 05:04:26', 'These are the people who really make the clinic run.\n\n[caption id="attachment_571" align="alignnone" width="205"]<a href="http://www.pacedermatology.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/Becky-At-Computer.jpg"><img class=" wp-image-571  " title="Becky At Computer" alt="" src="http://www.pacedermatology.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/Becky-At-Computer-570x855.jpg" width="205" height="308" /></a> Becky Coen - Office Manager[/caption]\n\nBecky Coen comes from a background of veterinary medicine. She spent many years working as an office manager at a large veterinary office in Puyallup. Now she has joined this medical clinic and brings a long list of crucial skills to the office.\n\nValerie Greenwood is one of our receptionists.  She does excellent work answering calls and checking everyone in and out.  It is always nice to see a kind friendly face.\n\nBrandy Bolton is a medical assistant.  This is her first time working in dermatology but she has picked it up very quickly.  She is friendly and caring and puts everyone at ease.\n\nCeirra Reynolds is a medical assistant as well and comes from a background of dermatology.  She is confident and clear and will be able to answer any questions.\n\nRobyn Lugo is the newest addition to the team. She has worked in derma', 'The Associates', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '84-autosave', '', '', '2013-01-01 22:04:26', '2013-01-02 05:04:26', '', 84, 'http://www.pacedermatology.com/84-autosave', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(1170, 1, '2012-10-30 22:33:48', '2012-10-31 05:33:48', 'These are the people who really make the clinic run.\r\n\r\n[caption id="attachment_571" align="alignnone" width="205" caption="Becky Coen - Office Manager"]<a href="http://www.pacedermatology.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/Becky-At-Computer.jpg"><img class=" wp-image-571  " title="Becky At Computer" src="http://www.pacedermatology.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/Becky-At-Computer-570x855.jpg" alt="" width="205" height="308" /></a>[/caption]\r\n\r\nBecky Coen comes from a background of veterinary medicine. She spent many years working as an office manager at a large veterinary office in Puyallup. Now she has joined this medical clinic and brings a long list of crucial skills to the office.\r\n\r\nValerie Greenwood is one of our receptionists.  She does excellent work answering calls and checking everyone in and out.  It is always nice to see a kind friendly face.\r\n\r\nBrandy Bolton is a medical assistant.  This is her first time working in dermatology but she has picked it up very quickly.  She is friendly and caring and puts everyone at ease.\r\n\r\nCeirra Reynolds is a medical assistant as well and comes from a background of dermatology.  She is confident and clear and will be able to answer any questions.\r\n\r\nMia Kimura is the newest addition to the team. After a number of years working behind the scenes in the medical field, Mia is excited to be back at the front working directly with patients. She is always happy to help!', 'The Associates', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '84-revision-13', '', '', '2012-10-30 22:33:48', '2012-10-31 05:33:48', '', 84, 'http://www.pacedermatology.com/84-revision-13/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
