(476, 1, '2011-09-17 18:05:35', '2011-09-17 18:05:35', 'We perform fillers and botulinum toxin injection as well as consult on ways to improve your skin''s appearance overall.  Some of the more common procedures we perform are listed below.  We strive to provide cost effective anti-aging procedures that provide the most improvement and have been shown with independent research studies to definitively reverse the effects of aging.  Every procedure is performed by a board certified dermatologist.\r\n\r\n<strong>Botulinum Toxin for wrinkles</strong> -This is probably one of the most satisfying cosmetic procedures that can be performed.  This is better known as Botox and Dysport.\r\n\r\n<strong>Injections and Fillers</strong> - Brand names of these products include Restalyne, Perlane, Juvederm, Radiesse, and Sculptra.\r\n\r\n<strong>Sclerotherapy for leg veins</strong>\r\n\r\n<strong>Chemical Peels</strong> - These are several different acids that can be applied.  The most commonly applied are glycolic and TCA.', 'Cosmetic', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '23-revision-7', '', '', '2011-09-17 18:05:35', '2011-09-17 18:05:35', '', 23, 'http://www.pacedermatology.com/23-revision-7', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(477, 1, '2011-09-17 18:06:18', '2011-09-17 18:06:18', 'We perform fillers and botulinum toxin injection as well as consult on ways to improve your skin''s appearance overall.  Some of the more common procedures we perform are listed below.  We strive to provide cost effective anti-aging procedures that provide the most improvement and have been shown with independent research studies to definitively reverse the effects of aging.  Every procedure is performed by a board certified dermatologist.\r\n\r\n<strong>Botulinum Toxin for wrinkles</strong> -This is probably one of the most satisfying cosmetic procedures that can be performed.  This is better known as Botox and Dysport.\r\n\r\n<strong>Injections and Fillers</strong> - Brand names of these products include Restylane, Perlane, Juvederm, Radiesse, and Sculptra.\r\n\r\n<strong>Sclerotherapy for leg veins</strong>\r\n\r\n<strong>Chemical Peels</strong> - These are several different acids that can be applied.  The most commonly applied are glycolic and TCA.', 'Cosmetic', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '23-revision-8', '', '', '2011-09-17 18:06:18', '2011-09-17 18:06:18', '', 23, 'http://www.pacedermatology.com/23-revision-8', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(478, 1, '2011-09-17 18:10:50', '2011-09-17 18:10:50', 'We perform fillers and botulinum toxin injection as well as consult on ways to improve your skin''s appearance overall.  Some of the more common procedures we perform are listed below.  We strive to provide cost effective anti-aging procedures that provide the most improvement and have been shown with independent research studies to definitively reverse the effects of aging.  Every procedure is performed by a board certified dermatologist.\r\n\r\n<strong>Botulinum Toxin for wrinkles</strong> -This is probably one of the most satisfying cosmetic procedures that can be performed.  This is better known as Botox and Dysport.\r\n\r\n<strong>Injections and Fillers</strong> - Brand names of these products include Restylane, Perlane, Juvederm, Radiesse, and Sculptra.\r\n\r\n<strong>Sclerotherapy for leg veins</strong> - This can be very effective for the right person with leg veins.  Sotradecol, sodium tetradecyl sulfate (STS) is used to sclerose the veins and is FDA approved for this purpose.<strong>\r\n</strong>\r\n\r\n<strong>Chemical Peels</strong> - These are several different acids that can be applied.  The most commonly applied are glycolic and TCA.', 'Cosmetic', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '23-revision-9', '', '', '2011-09-17 18:10:50', '2011-09-17 18:10:50', '', 23, 'http://www.pacedermatology.com/23-revision-9', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(479, 1, '2011-09-17 18:18:49', '2011-09-17 18:18:49', 'We perform fillers and botulinum toxin injection as well as consult on ways to improve your skin''s appearance overall.  Some of the more common procedures we perform are listed below.  We strive to provide cost effective anti-aging procedures that provide the most improvement and have been shown with independent research studies to definitively reverse the effects of aging.  Every procedure is performed by a board certified dermatologist.\r\n\r\n<strong>Botulinum Toxin for wrinkles</strong> -This is probably one of the most satisfying cosmetic procedures that can be performed.  This is better known as Botox and Dysport.  This works for the lines on the forehead and between the eyes, as well as crows feet and some lines on the lower face.  It can also be used to soften large chewing and cheek muscles and give the face a slimmer appearance.  It can help to give eyes a more rounded appearance.\r\n\r\n<strong>Injections and Fillers</strong> - Brand names of these products include Restylane, Perlane, Juvederm, Radiesse, and Sculptra.  These compounds include hyaluronic acid (HA), calcium hydroxyapatite, and poly-L-lactic acid.  They are primarily used to fill deeper lines around the mouth and provide a "liquid" face lift when injected in the cheeks, cheekbones, and temples.\r\n\r\n<strong>Sclerotherapy for leg veins</strong> - This can be very effective for the right person with leg veins.  Sotradecol, sodium tetradecyl sulfate (STS) is used to sclerose the veins and is FDA approved for this purpose.<strong>\r\n</strong>\r\n\r\n<strong>Chemical Peels</strong> - These are several different acids that can be applied.  The most commonly applied are glycolic and TCA.', 'Cosmetic', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '23-revision-10', '', '', '2011-09-17 18:18:49', '2011-09-17 18:18:49', '', 23, 'http://www.pacedermatology.com/23-revision-10', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
