(574, 1, '2012-03-25 22:15:22', '2012-03-25 22:15:22', 'These are the people who really make the clinic run.\r\n\r\n[caption id="attachment_439" align="alignnone" width="200" caption="Becky Coen - Office Manager"]<a href="http://www.pacedermatology.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/10/L1000255.jpg"><img class="size-thumbnail wp-image-439" title="Becky Coen" src="http://www.pacedermatology.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/10/L1000255-200x178.jpg" alt="" width="200" height="178" /></a>[/caption]\r\n\r\nBecky Coen comes from a background of veterinary medicine. She spent many years working as an office manager at a large veterinary office in Puyallup. Now she has joined this medical clinic and brings a long list of crucial skills to the office.\r\n\r\nValerie Greenwood is our receptionist.  She does excellent work answering calls and checking everyone in and out.  It is always nice to see a kind friendly face.\r\n\r\nBrandy Bolton is a medical assistant.  This is her first time working in dermatology but she has picked it up very quickly.  She is friendly and caring and puts everyone at ease.\r\n\r\nCeirra Reynolds is a medical assistant as well and comes from a background of dermatology.  She is confident and clear and will be able to answer any questions.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', 'The Associates', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '84-revision-9', '', '', '2012-03-25 22:15:22', '2012-03-25 22:15:22', '', 84, 'http://www.pacedermatology.com/84-revision-9', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
