(581, 1, '2012-03-25 22:17:47', '2012-03-25 22:17:47', '[caption id="attachment_391" align="alignnone" width="200" caption="Aaron K. Pace, M.D."]<a href="http://www.pacedermatology.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/04/Aaron-Headshot.jpg"><img class="size-thumbnail wp-image-391" title="Dr. Pace" src="http://www.pacedermatology.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/04/Aaron-Headshot-200x168.jpg" alt="" width="200" height="168" /></a>[/caption]\r\n\r\nDr. Pace is a board certified dermatologist and began the practice, it opened in July of 2011. He graduated from Steilacoom high school and went Occidental College in Los Angeles, California, then went to medical school at Loyola University Chicago, Stritch School of Medicine. After medical school he completed his internship at MacNeal Hospital in Berwyn, Illinois prior to beginning his dermatology residency. Dr. Pace returned to Loyola for his dermatology residency in Chicago, Illinois. Now he has returned to practice dermatology and serve the community that he grew up in.\r\n\r\nOn a more personal note, Dr. Pace enjoys spending time with his wife and children, two girls and their youngest, a boy, and their dogs.\r\n\r\nCurrently Dr. Aaron K. Pace is the only physician at the clinic, however, Dr. Andrew P. Pace, his younger brother, will be finishing a dermatology residency in June of 2013 and he will be joining the practice at that time.  He does visit the clinic occasionally so you may have the opportunity to meet him prior to this.', 'The Doctor', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '26-revision-14', '', '', '2012-03-25 22:17:47', '2012-03-25 22:17:47', '', 26, 'http://www.pacedermatology.com/26-revision-14', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
