e as prescription ointments or creams, always apply the prescription medication first.\r\n11. Do not wear tight or rough clothing. Wool clothes and new clothes can be irritating.\r\n12. Avoid saunas and steam baths\r\n13. For extreme dryness, a humidifier or vaporizer may help. Remember to keep it clean or molds may spread throughout the humidified area.', 'Dry Skin in the Fall and Winter', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '875-revision-4', '', '', '2012-09-21 07:41:56', '2012-09-21 14:41:56', '', 875, 'http://www.pacedermatology.com/875-revision-4/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
