(1057, 1, '2012-10-13 17:44:44', '2012-10-14 00:44:44', 'Call (253) 572-2842 to book a free consult and get ready to say hello to less shaving, more youthful, natural, and brighter skin. Pace dermatology is committed to bringing state of the art dermatology to the Pacific Northwest. In achieving this goal we currently use three different lasers.\r\n\r\n<a title="Laser Hair Removal" href="http://www.pacedermatology.com/services/laser-hair-removal/">Diode Laser</a> - Ideal for hair removal.\r\n\r\n<a title="IPL Skin Rejuvenation" href="http://www.pacedermatology.com/services/ipl-skin-rejuvenation/">Intense Pulse Light (IPL)</a> - The broadest functionality of our devices, for photofacials, brown spots, redness, blood vessels and hair removal.  It can also be used for photodynamic therapy to treat per-cancerous actinic keratoses.\r\n\r\n<a title="Laser Vein Removal" href="http://www.pacedermatology.com/services/lasers/laser-vein-removal/">Nd:YAG Laser</a> - For the treatment of superficial blood vessels.\r\n\r\nLasers are powerful devices and not appropriate for everyone so we do require a free consult to get you setup for your treatments.  Laser treatments are not covered by insurance.', 'Laser', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '1031-revision-4', '', '', '2012-10-13 17:44:44', '2012-10-14 00:44:44', '', 1031, 'http://www.pacedermatology.com/1031-revision-4/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
