(1125, 1, '2012-10-30 22:28:33', '2012-10-31 05:28:33', '[caption id="attachment_569" align="alignleft" width="274"]<a href="http://www.pacedermatology.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/Aaron-Pace-Window-Background.jpg"><img class="wp-image-569 " title="Aaron Pace Window Background" src="http://www.pacedermatology.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/Aaron-Pace-Window-Background-570x854.jpg" alt="" width="274" height="410" /></a> Aaron K. Pace, M.D.[/caption]\r\n\r\nDr. Pace is a board certified dermatologist and began the practice, it opened in July of 2011.  He graduated from Steilacoom high school and went Occidental College in Los Angeles, California, then went to medical school at Loyola University Chicago, Stritch School of Medicine.  After medical school he completed his internship at MacNeal Hospital in Berwyn, Illinois prior to beginning his dermatology residency.  Dr. Pace returned to Loyola for his dermatology residency in Chicago, Illinois.  Now he has returned to practice dermatology and serve the community that he grew up in.\r\n\r\nOn a more personal note, Dr. Pace enjoys spending time with his wife and three children.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n\r\n<iframe width="560" height="315" src="http://www.youtube.com/embed/80alO87Us2A" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n\r\n[caption id="attachment_568" align="alignnone" width="274"]<a href="http://www.pacedermatology.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/Aaron-Pace-Microscope.jpg"><img class=" wp-image-568  " title="Aaron Pace Microscope" src="http://www.pacedermatology.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/Aaron-Pace-Microscope-570x855.jpg" alt="" width="274" height="410" /></a> Working at the Microscope[/caption]\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', 'About', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'about', '', '', '2012-10-30 22:32:50', '2012-10-31 05:32:50', '', 0, 'http://www.pacedermatology.com/?page_id=1125', 0, 'page', '', 0),
