(1135, 1, '2012-09-27 16:15:22', '2012-09-27 23:15:22', 'If you have a tattoo you regret theres a good chance your dermatologist can get it removed but there are several factors that come into play. Studies show that it will be harder to remove if:\r\n\r\n1. Its large, covering over 12 inches.\r\n\r\n2. Its colorful, ink colors other than black or red are more difficult.\r\n\r\n3. Its old, more than 3 years.\r\n\r\n4. If you smoke, smoking impairs wound healing processes.\r\n\r\n5. If it is on your feet or legs.\r\n\r\nRead full article at <a href="http://www.freep.com/article/20120919/FEATURES08/120919015/1025/features">freep.com</a>', 'Think Before You Ink', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '927-revision-3', '', '', '2012-09-27 16:15:22', '2012-09-27 23:15:22', '', 927, 'http://www.pacedermatology.com/927-revision-3/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
