(1190, 1, '2013-01-26 11:35:55', '2013-01-26 18:35:55', 'This past Friday, we had our first annual staff retreat.  We focused on how to improve patient care and make the overall visit more convenient and less stressful for our patients.  Our staff worked hard to learn how to work better together and improve our ability to communicate.  We also worked on practical aspects of our jobs like setting up for procedures, surgeries, and laser treatments.  Dr. Pace gave a talk on some of the basic points of dermatology so some of our non-medical staff could improve their understanding of the basic principles of dermatology.  Enjoy the photo gallery, we learned a lot and worked hard and hope you will see the improvements around the clinic.\r\n\r\n[gallery columns="4" ids="1212,1213,1214,1215,1216,1217,1218,1219,1220,1221,1222,1223,1224,1225,1226,1227,1228"]', 'Staff Retreat 2013', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'staff-retreat-2013', '', '', '2013-02-06 11:19:17', '2013-02-06 18:19:17', '', 0, 'http://www.pacedermatology.com/?p=1190', 0, 'post', '', 0),
